						<div class="postbody">Now that you have controls, you can run individual tests in nestest. Do all official instructions pass?<br /><br />You don't need to implement SBC as a separate opcode. It's the same as ADC, except the memory operand is EOR'd with #$FF first. If it's not in SBC, it might be in CMP.</div>

