					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Proper handling of flags on the stack is essential for Galaxian.<br /><br />There is no &quot;U flag&quot; that I know of, but bit 5 of P is always pushed as 1. PHP and BRK always push B (bit 4 of P) as 1, and /IRQ and /NMI push it as 0. PLP and RTI ignore bits 5 and 4.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

