be a tiny bug I haven't noticed somewhere in the program which makes it go into a branch where it shouldn't go, as it ends up jumping to $03A0 at the end, which shouldn't happen. I'll try fixing that tomorrow, and if I'm lucky I'll hit 2 birds with one stone and it will fix the glitchy Mario Bros behavior too. I doubt it though, but who knows. If anyone has any other suggestions, please keep them coming.</div>

